</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>
<persName>趙俊</persName>字<name key="趙俊" type="zi">德進</name>
<pc>，</pc>南京宋城人<pc>。</pc>
<date when="1097">
<date notBefore="1094" notAfter="1098">紹聖</date>
<measure quantity="4" unit="years">
<num value="4">四</num>年</measure>
</date>
<term>進士</term>
<pc>，</pc>官至朝奉郎<pc>。</pc>隱居杜門<pc>，</pc>雖鄉裏不妄交<pc>。</pc>劉安世無恙時居河南<pc>，</pc>暇則獨<num value="1">一</num>過之<pc>。</pc>徐處仁與<name key="趙俊" type="givenName">俊</name>厚善<pc>，</pc>及為丞相<pc>，</pc>鄉人多見用<pc>，</pc>
