</div>
<div>
<p>劉化源<pc>，</pc>
<placeName>耀州</placeName>人<pc>。</pc>
<date notBefore="1094" notAfter="1098">紹聖</date>元年<term>進士</term>
<pc>。</pc>
<date notBefore="1127" notAfter="1130">建炎</date>初<pc>，</pc>金人陷關陝<pc>，</pc>守令以城降者<pc>，</pc>金人因而命之<pc>。</pc>化源時知<placeName>隴州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>不肯降<pc>，</pc>城陷被執<pc>。</pc>金人使人守之<pc>，</pc>不得死<pc>，</pc>遂驅入河北<pc>，</pc>鬻蔬果<pc>、</pc>隱民間者<measure quantity="10" unit="years">
